these has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act, then I appoint the other to
be the sole executor of my estate.
{{/if}}

{{#if executorThree}}
[2 Executors acting independently]
(a) I appoint {{executor}} of {{executorCity}}, {{executorProvince}}, and {{altExecutor}}
