one of these has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act, then I appoint the
other to be the sole executor of my estate.
{{/if}}

{{#if altExecutorOne}}
[1 Alternate Executor]
(b) If my executor first named has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act,
then I appoint {{altExecutor}} of {{altExecutorCity}}, {{altExecutorProvince}} as the sole
