However, if one of these has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act, then I
appoint the other to be the sole executor of my estate.
{{/if}}

{{#if altExecutorThree}}
[2 Alternate Executors acting independently]
(b) If my executor first named has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act,
then I appoint {{altExecutor}} of {{altExecutorCity}}, {{altExecutorProvince}}, and {{alt2Executor}}
of {{alt2ExecutorCity}}, {{alt2ExecutorProvince}}, as co-executors of my
estate, with authority to act independent of each other. This grants either of them the power to
make decisions and take actions concerning the administration of my estate without the need
for joint approval, ensuring flexibility and efficiency in managing my estate as per my wishes.
However, if one of these has not survived me, or at any time is unable or unwilling to act, then I
appoint the other to be the sole executor of my estate.
{{/if}}

{{#if altAltExecutor}}
[Alternate Alternate Executor]
(c) If both my executors named above have not survived me, or at any time are unable or
unwilling to act, then I appoint {{alt2Executor}} of {{alt2ExecutorCity}}, {{alt2ExecutorProvince}}
