{{/if}}

4. PAYMENT OF DEBTS AND TAXES

I direct my executor or executors to pay as soon as convenient after my death all debts, funeral
and testamentary expenses and taxes that my estate is legally bound to pay, or to commute,
prepay or defer payment of such debts or taxes as my executor or executors may in his, her, or
their sole and absolute discretion consider advisable, and I hereby empower my executor or
executors to make any election, determination, or designation pursuant to the Income Tax Act or
any other taxing statute or any regulation pursuant thereto.

5. DISPOSITION OF PROPERTY

I give all the residue of my property, both real and personal, and including any property over
which I may have a general power of appointment, to the executor or executors UPON THE
FOLLOWING TRUSTS, namely:

Personal articles

(a) to divide all articles of a personal, domestic, or household use or ornament or works of
art, not specifically referred to elsewhere in this my Last Will, in accordance with a list,
memorandum, or letter signed by me, which I may leave among my personal papers or
attached to a copy of this my Last Will;

Specific gifts

{{#if giftList}}
(b) to give and transfer each of the following items to the person named for his or her
exclusive and absolute use:
{{#each gifts}}
({{inc @index}}) {{this.gift}} to {{this.recipient}};
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if gift}}
(b) to give and transfer {{gifts.[0].gift}} to {{gifts.[0].recipient}} for {{pronoun}} exclusive and absolute use.
{{/if}}

{{#if petCare}}
(b.1) to give and transfer the sum of ${{petCareAmount}} to the person selected by my Executor to
care for any pets I own at the time of my death, with the request that the funds be used for
the care and well-being of those pets. I leave this request to the discretion of my Executor
and the selected caregiver;
{{/if}}

{{#if hensonTrust}}
(b.2) to give and transfer {{hensonAmount}} of the residue of my estate to my executor, to be held in
trust in accordance with the Henson Trust provisions set out in this Will for the benefit of
{{hensonBenificiary}}.
{{/if}}

{{#if lifeTenant}}
Life Interest in Real Property

(b.3) If {{lifeTenant}} survives me, I direct my Executor to hold any interest (the “Residential
Property”) I have in lands and buildings at {{residentialAddress}}, subject to any financial encumbrances against
the Residential Property (other than any charges for deferred property taxes), and:

(i) permit {{lifeTenant}} to use and enjoy the Residential Property as long as {{lifeTenantPronoun}} lives,
subject to certain conditions, including the responsibility to:

A. keep the Residential Property insured;
B. pay local taxes; and
C. cover maintenance costs.

{{#if lifeTenantDistribute}}
(ii) Upon {{lifeTenant}}'s death or earlier inability or unwillingness to reside in the Residential Property,
I direct my Executor to sell the Residential Property and distribute the proceeds to / among the
following, or as many of them as survive me, share and share alike: {{lifeTenantDistributeList}}.
{{/if}}

{{#if lifeTenantTransfer}}
(ii) Upon {{lifeTenant}}'s death or earlier inability or unwillingness to reside in the Residential Property,
I direct my Executor to transfer the Residential Property to {{lifeTenantTransferRecipiant}};
{{/if}}

{{#if lifeTenantRest}}
(ii) Upon {{lifeTenant}}'s death or earlier inability or unwillingness to reside in the Residential Property,
I direct my Executor to add the Residential Property, or proceeds from the sale thereof, to the rest
and residue of my estate.
{{/if}}
{{/if}}

Rest and residue

{{#if residueToExecutor}}
(c) to give the rest and residue of my estate to {{executor}}.
{{/if}}
{{#if residueToChildren}}
(c) to divide the rest and residue of my estate among my surviving children, share and share alike.
{{/if}}
{{#if residueToSiblings}}
(c) to divide the rest and residue of my estate among my surviving siblings, share and share alike.
{{/if}}
{{#if residueToList}}
(c) to divide the rest and residue of my estate among the following, or as many of them as
survive me, share and share alike: {{residueList}}.
{{/if}}
{{#if residueShares}}
(c) to divide the residue of my estate into equal shares which shall be distributed among the
following, or as many of them as survive me:
{{#each residueRecipients}}
   ({{inc @index}}) {{this.name}} shall receive {{this.shares}} shares{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
{{/each}}.
{{/if}}

Gift over

{{#if fallbackToNamedPerson}}
(d) in the event {{executor}} fails to survive me, to give the rest and residue of my estate to {{fallbackPerson}}.
{{/if}}
{{#if fallbackToChildren}}
(d) in the event {{executor}} fails to survive me, to divide the rest and residue of my estate among my
surviving children, share and share alike.
{{/if}}
{{#if fallbackToSiblings}}
(d) in the event {{executor}} fails to survive me, to divide the rest and residue of my estate among my
